{"tid":2350921,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"越南新增8宗輸入病例 ，1人從台灣入境","createTime":"2021-01-02T17:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T01:14:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"97f0dcb0d848eb2145f2d07b9b50400b6b008fee","tid":2350921,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T17:55:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568336-20210103.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568336-20210103.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb01pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=399e211b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568336-20210103.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=cf9d0a93\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568336-20210103.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n越南昨晚通報新增8 宗境外輸入新型肺炎確診病例，全部患者都是越南人，其中一人從台灣入境。<br />\n<br />\n這名34歲女子上周三乘坐越竹航空班機抵達越南南部的芹苴機場，入境後在前江省接受隔離，元旦日對病毒檢測呈陽性。<br />\n<br />\n另外，越南早前發現一宗英國流行的變種新型冠狀病毒個案，患者是一名上月從英國入境的越南公民。<br />\n<br />\n越南累計1482人確診，35人死亡。"},{"pid":"8e1b0e12034274f0ec70fd265e64efe6ef20f7e2","tid":2350921,"uid":26424,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T18:28:43.000Z","msg":"A,喺飛機上感染<br />\nB,隔離期間感染<br />\nC,越南檢測方法有誤<br />\nD,入境台灣前已經感染(期間不具傳染性)離開台灣後發病<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n四個解釋買定離手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28772d4a220bd39cf1e28cac3577f94b51e5b9bb","tid":2350921,"uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T20:44:58.000Z","msg":"其實飛機同機場真係好多病毒 🦠"},{"pid":"ebab5766c9636d5a795eafc19b0070ade098a282","tid":2350921,"uid":105976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T01:14:37.000Z","msg":"將中國同台灣分開計?!<br />\n傷害